    "title": "躊躇わず、その輝きへ手を伸ばす",
    "enTitle": "Don't Stop, Reach For That Brilliance",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――休日の昼下がり。外出先でアイに出会うなり、\nあるクイズのペアチャレンジに付き合ってほしいと頼まれた。",
            "enText": "——It was late in the afternoon of a day off. While out and about, I \nran in to Ai. She asked me to be her partner in a Quiz Challenge duo.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -4951585590053912592
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 277,
                    "pathId": 267617397642002055
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 7770719827591461911
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -330058567385117765,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "お店に入ったら、ちょうど開催してて……\n全問正解だと、キューまるのペア人形をもらえるの！　お願いっ！",
            "enText": "When I entered the shop, there was a contest \nhappening……If you answer all the question correctly, \nyou get a pair of Kyumaru dolls! So please!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 242,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "キューまる……？",
                    "enText": "Kyumaru……?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -7639605732996739141
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7858259438715207980
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9149984611645198731,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "このほんわかした感じの、きゅうりを持ったカッパの子よ。\nとってもかわいいでしょ♪",
            "enText": "This cute and cozy Kappa carrying a cucumber. \nIsn't it really cute♪?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 194,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 281,
                    "pathId": 1574749173794147104
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 221627287943856248
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8697184517060958372,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "わたし、キューまるのことが昔から大好きで……だからお願い！",
            "enText": "I've always really liked Kyumaru, since a long time ago……so please!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 212,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいよ、俺でよければ",
                    "enText": "Sure, if you don't mind",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいよ、私でよければ",
                    "enText": "Sure, if you don't mind",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -2798286642759686273
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -5449516554288456734
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1215920193359485861,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――次の問題の解答者は、トレーナーね。\nビギナーズラック、信じてるわよ！",
            "enText": "——You're the one that needs to answer the next \nquestion, Trainer. Let's believe in Beginner's Luck!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 202,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 409628530321231897
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 1408939019434049032
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2508075363542980084,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ショップの店長",
            "enName": "Shop Staff",
            "jpText": "では問題です！　こちらのカッパのキューまる――の隣に住む、\nパフィンおじさんの姪が飼っているクマノミの名前はなんでしょう？",
            "enText": "And here's your question! This Kappa, Kyumaru's—— \nNeighbor, Uncle Puffin has a niece. What is the \nname of the clownfish she keeps as a pet?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 317,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 349,
                    "pathId": 2991125551740390778
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8648332994970049539
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4328412077162089868,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ちょ、ちょっと！\nその問題、トレーナーにはコアすぎるわよ……！",
            "enText": "W-wait a minute! \nThat question is to core for Trainer-san……!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 160,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（わ、わかるか～！！）クマちゃん、とか？",
                    "enText": "(Like hell I'd know～!!) Is it Tama-chan?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -6663494980443508786
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8138361556559872076,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ショップの店長",
            "enName": "Shop Staff",
            "jpText": "残念っ、不正解！　これにて今回のチャレンジは終了です！\nよかったらまた挑戦してくださいね～！",
            "enText": "Unfortunately, that's incorrect! \nAnd so this challenge comes to an end! Feel free to try again～!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 290,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "あぁぁぁぁ～……",
                    "enText": "Aww～……",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": -2515570998045434050
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -5592964352893149373
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -366335103629177101,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ほんっと悔しい！\nまさか、あんなコアな問題ばかりだなんて！",
            "enText": "It's so frustrating! To think they'd \nask so many core questions like that!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 200,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "力になれなくてごめん……",
                    "enText": "Sorry I couldn't help much……",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -1268027247212915333
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 6889386847371189978
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3121914835032724946,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "しょうがないわよ、気にしないで！\nあんなの、熱心なキューまるファンでも答えられるかどうか……。",
            "enText": "It can't be helped, don't worry about it. \nA question like that, I don't think most of \neven the die hard fans would be able to answer it……",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 247,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 197,
                    "pathId": 7272680869949848550
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": -5983202328558087059
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7267290975227084093,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "フォローしてくれるアーモンドアイだが、\nその表情からはチャレンジに失敗した悔しさがにじみ出ている。",
            "enText": "Almond Eye was trying to be considerate, but it was pretty \nobvious by her expression that she was frustrated at losing.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……じゃあ、今度はがっつり準備しよう！",
                    "enText": "……Then, let's prepare for a rematch!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 197,
                    "pathId": 5288386968841353406
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": -4807152604379183098
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3564047611758560410,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "えっ？　今度って――",
            "enText": "Ehh? Next time——",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 197,
                    "pathId": -9218771206246989755
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5024577609409732178
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5774595301003112983,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "トレーナー、また付き合ってくれるの……？",
            "enText": "Trainer, will you go with me next time……?",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "もちろん。やろうよ、リベンジ！",
                    "enText": "Of course. Let's get our revenge!",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -8320600758801769819
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2755991255385468433,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……っ！！\nええ、望むところよ！　次こそ全問正解してみせるわ！",
            "enText": "……!! Yeah, that's what I wanna hear! \nNext time we'll get all of them right!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 207,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 4528054597057259146
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -4478331594876305331
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5755874868621708416,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "思い立ったら即行動、ということでアーモンドアイに連れられて、\n難問クイズに向けた勉強を行うことになった。",
            "enText": "We acted immediately on that idea. \nAlmond Eye and I headed to a place to study for the quiz ahead.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 160,
                    "pathId": -3835436216948643752
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -728061847106295211,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ここのカラオケ、映像作品の再生もできるのよ。\n――過去の劇場版アニメ、一緒に観ましょう？",
            "enText": "At this Karaoke place, you can even play videos. \n——Shall we watch some of the older Anime movies together?",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 241,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -83519433658863850
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8340968893649037536
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1718091754745868228,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ふふ……♪　やっぱりキューまるはかわいいわね。\nきゅうりが好きってところも、シンパシー感じちゃう。",
            "enText": "Fufu……♪ Kyumaru really is cute, right? \nReally liking cucumbers, I can sympathize with that.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 275,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "だからキューまるが好きなのか？",
                    "enText": "Is that why you like Kyumaru?",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "だからキューまるが好きなの？",
                    "enText": "Is that why you like Kyumaru?",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
