            "pathId": 5889062094607641880,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "うーん……それもあるけど。生き別れのお母さんを探すためなら、\nどんな困難にも真っすぐ挑む強さがいいと思うわ。",
            "enText": "Hmmm……that's a part of it, but also, how, in order to \nfind his long-lost mother, he's honestly working to \nget stronger to face any challenge that comes his way.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 333,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "目標に向かって一直線……アイみたいだね",
                    "enText": "Straight for their goal……Just like Ai",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
