            "pathId": -6992541821495185436,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "あら、そうかも。……あっ、観て。このシーンは特にオススメ！\nお母さんのためにって勇気を振り絞るキューまるがたまらないの。",
            "enText": "Oh, that might be it too. ……Ah, look. I really \nrecommend watching this scene! The way Kyumaru \nmusters up his courage for the sake of his mother is great.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 303,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": 7575589876299192678
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 276,
                    "pathId": -9015318273282063035
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2320868392968241508,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……あら？\nトレーナー、ちょっと目が赤いわよ？　大丈夫？",
            "enText": "……Huh? \nTrainer, your eyes are kind of red, you know? Are you okay?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 218,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "最後のシーンが、胸にきて……",
                    "enText": "That last scene was so moving……",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
