            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 324972125377458497
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -6417414705925886946
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2443996762285747224,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ああ、あれね……！\nわたしも初めて観た時は、うるっときちゃったわ。",
            "enText": "Oh, that one, huh……! \nThe first time I saw it, my eyes welled up too.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 198,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": -4925319489157384761
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -3092311540208734257
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4798959204511965759,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "でも……つらい別れが訪れても、お母さんのために旅を続ける。\nキューまるの強さを再確認できた作品だったわ。",
            "enText": "But……even though it's painful to be apart, for his mother he continues \nhis journey. It was a story that reaffirmed Kyumaru's strength.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 313,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 348,
                    "pathId": 3738566833962478078
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": -7610930184986430015
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -480442433162427865,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――さて。ひと通り観終わったことだし、\nクイズに出そうな情報をまとめた後は、次に行きましょうか！",
            "enText": "——Alright. Now that the movie is over, let's review \nand think about some potential questions that might \nshow up on the quiz! That's our next step!",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 237,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "次って？",
                    "enText": "Next……?",
                    "nextBlock": 24
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 259,
                    "pathId": 1181322836195326288
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 279,
                    "pathId": 6920802294508098678
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 627334650555176619,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "コラボカフェ！　そろそろお昼も近づいてきたし、\n勉強もできて一石二鳥でしょ？",
            "enText": "A Collab Cafe! It's getting close to lunchtime \nso it'll be like two birds with one stone, right?",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 215,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -1864302915630634260
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3395285526761264785
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2636866901031414674,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "アザラシ伯爵のクリームパンケーキに、トド助のオムそば――\nすごく迷ったけど、どっちも頼んで正解だったわ♪",
            "enText": "Earl Seal's cream pankcakes or Todosuke's omelette soba——It was a \nreally hard choice, but getting them both was the correct decision♪",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 268,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
