            "pathId": -1597767303048121741,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "あ、トレーナーのよくばりプレートもかわいいわね……！\nちょっと写真撮らせてもらえない？",
            "enText": "Ah, Trainer's Greedy Plate is really cute too……! \nCan I take a picture of it?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
